{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1187840/extras/Vesper_IntroductionZL.gif?t=1654161275\" /><br><br><strong>A visionary and mysterious adventure taking place in a decaying world</strong> full of secrets to uncover, where your choices will change the future of an entire race.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1187840/extras/Vesper_EscapeScenesZL.gif?t=1654161275\" /><br><br>A small android called Seven is lost on <strong>an eerie planet full of perils and traces of an ancient civilization</strong>, with no powers and no ability to defeat enemies until he finds the Drive Gun, <strong>a weapon used to absorb lights, create darkness, and control minds.</strong>  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1187840/extras/Vesper_PickingDriveGunZL.gif?t=1654161275\" /><br><br><strong>Use the Drive Gun to absorb light</strong> from various sources and <strong>create dark spots</strong> in which you can hide. <strong>Inject absorbed light into machineries</strong> to open portals and activate deadly traps.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1187840/extras/Vesper_ControlEnemiesZL.gif?t=1654161275\" /><br><br><strong>Control your opponents with light</strong> <strong>and dispose of them after have exploited their abilities.</strong><br>Take control of your destiny and decide the future of the Android\u2019s race.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1187840/extras/Vesper_LandscapeChurchZL.gif?t=1654161275\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Creative Solutions</strong>: solve puzzles and trick your enemies in multiple ways using the power of the Drive Gun<br></li><li><strong>Connecting the Dots</strong>: collect mysterious and encrypted 